de.tub.reader.file
Class TextFileLineReader

java.lang.Object
  de.tub.observer.Subject
      de.tub.reader.file.TextFileLineReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITextFileReader, IReader, Cloneable
public class TextFileLineReader
extends Subject
implements ITextFileReader, Cloneable

This reader reads a file with the given name from the file system line by line and delegates the processing of each line to the given processor. An offset can be specified to ignore a certain amount of lines from the beginning of the file.

The TextFileLineReader notifies its observers about its finishing of reading a file.

Author:
Sebastian Oelke
